snippet.title: Memetown USA Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The official Blasted Science role-playing game is coming out August 30, 2018!

Memetown Website: https://www.memetownusa.com

Buy it on Steam August 30:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/911100/Memetown_USA/

(You will be able to find it on Game Jolt as well)

Music Credit:
Epic Sax Guy Remix by WYKO
https://soundcloud.com/wykomusic
https://twitter.com/wykomusic
